knocked out the power lines.

1:11:09.750 --> 1:11:10.833
I'll try the fuse box.

1:11:12.916 --> 1:11:15.625
-[booms of thunder]
-[sharp footsteps]

1:11:18.708 --> 1:11:21.625
[♪♪♪]

1:11:29.125 --> 1:11:30.791
[Jennifer] [cries] No.

1:11:30.791 --> 1:11:33.041
Daddy, no, no, no!
Please, Daddy, no, no, no, no!

1:11:33.041 --> 1:11:34.583
Daddy, please, please! Daddy!

1:11:34.583 --> 1:11:36.708
[screaming]
Mitch! Mitch, help me.

1:11:36.708 --> 1:11:39.083
Daddy, please.
-Oh, my God.

1:11:39.083 --> 1:11:41.041
-Where do you think
you're taking my husband?

1:11:41.041 --> 1:11:43.333
-You fucking bitch!

1:11:43.333 --> 1:11:45.333
What did you do to him?

1:11:45.333 --> 1:11:46.458
-What did I do?

1:11:47.958 --> 1:11:49.791
I think the question
the police are gonna ask is,

1:11:49.791 --> 1:11:51.416
"What did you do?"

1:11:51.416 --> 1:11:53.458
-No. They'll never believe you.
I-I have evidence.

1:11:53.458 --> 1:11:55.666
Evidence that proves
who you really are.

1:11:55.666 --> 1:11:57.500
-Oh, yeah?

1:11:57.500 --> 1:11:59.833
You mean that little file
Victor put together on me?

1:12:01.833 --> 1:12:03.500
Yeah, I took care of it already.

1:12:04.833 --> 1:12:06.875
Took care of him...

1:12:06.875 --> 1:12:09.708
and your rapist
pig of a brother too.

1:12:09.708 --> 1:12:10.916
-Fuck you!
-[Aileen groans]

1:12:10.916 --> 1:12:13.666
[loud thunderclap]

1:12:13.666 --> 1:12:15.916
[Jennifer] Here, help me.
Help me. We gotta get him up.

1:12:15.916 --> 1:12:16.916
[Mitch] One,

1:12:16.916 --> 1:12:18.041
two,

1:12:18.041 --> 1:12:21.166
three.
-[Lewis grunts]

1:12:21.166 --> 1:12:22.666
-[Jennifer] Let's go.
-[Mitch] Okay, come on.

1:12:22.666 --> 1:12:24.000
Let's go. Come on.
-[Jennifer] You got it.

1:12:24.000 --> 1:12:26.666
-[Lewis groans]
-Watch your step.

1:12:26.666 --> 1:12:27.958
-[Jennifer] Be careful.

1:12:29.416 --> 1:12:31.666
You'll be okay, Lewis.

1:12:31.666 --> 1:12:32.750
We're gonna get you out of here.

1:12:35.541 --> 1:12:37.166
All right, come on.
Just a little bit farther.

1:12:37.166 --> 1:12:38.625
-[Jennifer] Hang on, Dad.
Please hang on.

1:12:40.625 --> 1:12:42.458
-[Mitch] This way.
-Get him to the hospital.

1:12:42.458 --> 1:12:44.541
I'll deal with Aileen.
-No!

1:12:44.541 --> 1:12:46.625
I am not leaving here
without you.

1:12:46.625 --> 1:12:48.708
-Goddammit, Mitch!
Get him outta here!

1:12:48.708 --> 1:12:50.541
Just go! Now!

1:12:54.666 --> 1:12:58.166
[dramatic music]

1:12:58.166 --> 1:13:01.083
[groans]

1:13:12.416 --> 1:13:13.666
[sharp clap of thunder]

1:13:24.083 --> 1:13:26.833
[panting]

1:13:33.750 --> 1:13:34.958
[loud crack of thunder]

1:13:34.958 --> 1:13:35.916
[Jennifer gasps]

1:13:42.750 --> 1:13:44.583
[glass shatters]

1:13:45.625 --> 1:13:46.833
[door squeaks]

1:14:08.916 --> 1:14:11.958
[heavy downpour]

1:14:11.958 --> 1:14:14.625
[sharp clap of thunder]

1:14:14.625 --> 1:14:17.500
[mysterious music]

1:14:20.958 --> 1:14:22.000
-[screams] Ahhh!

1:14:22.000 --> 1:14:23.166
[Aileen screams]

1:14:23.166 --> 1:14:25.625
[water splashing]

1:14:25.625 --> 1:14:27.625
[Aileen gasps]

1:14:27.625 --> 1:14:30.541
[Aileen panting]

1:14:31.666 --> 1:14:32.708
-I can't swim.

1:14:33.958 --> 1:14:35.625
-Take my hand.

1:14:37.750 --> 1:14:39.625
Lee, here.

1:14:39.625 --> 1:14:41.000
Reach.

1:14:41.000 --> 1:14:42.208
[Aileen] I can't.

1:14:45.666 --> 1:14:46.875
[Aileen panting and gasps]

1:14:46.875 --> 1:14:48.666
[Jennifer screams]

1:14:50.250 --> 1:14:52.958
[Aileen panting]

1:14:57.958 --> 1:14:59.750
[Jennifer gasps]

1:15:01.833 --> 1:15:04.083
[Jennifer squealing]

1:15:04.083 --> 1:15:06.541
[Aileen gasps]

1:15:07.666 --> 1:15:09.875
[Jennifer gasping]

1:15:09.875 --> 1:15:12.166
[splashing desperately]

1:15:12.166 --> 1:15:14.875
[Jennifer gasping]

1:15:40.250 --> 1:15:43.125
[short blasts of thunder]

1:15:52.708 --> 1:15:55.250
[♪♪♪]

1:15:58.375 --> 1:16:01.250
[♪♪♪]

1:16:20.083 --> 1:16:21.375
[gasps]

1:16:21.375 --> 1:16:24.291
[panting]

1:16:31.708 --> 1:16:34.666
[claps of thunder]

1:16:34.666 --> 1:16:36.916
[panting]

1:16:36.916 --> 1:16:38.833
-[shouts] Aileen!

1:16:40.958 --> 1:16:43.041
[flashing thunderbolt]

1:16:54.291 --> 1:16:55.791
I see you, Aileen.

1:17:06.458 --> 1:17:08.208
It's over.
There's no way out!

1:17:10.958 --> 1:17:13.000
-I coulda been like you!

1:17:13.000 --> 1:17:14.208
You're no better than me

1:17:14.208 --> 1:17:16.416
just 'cause you were
born into money!

1:17:16.416 --> 1:17:18.166
You know,
I coulda been someone too!

1:17:20.000 --> 1:17:21.958
I have nothin'! I am nothin'!

1:17:24.416 --> 1:17:26.125
-It's over, Aileen.

1:17:31.958 --> 1:17:33.083
[Jennifer] Oh, God, please.

1:17:33.083 --> 1:17:34.750
-You're just as stupid as a man.

1:17:34.750 --> 1:17:35.666
-Aileen!

1:17:36.708 --> 1:17:38.041
[cane clanks]

1:17:38.041 --> 1:17:39.250
-[boom goes "Whoosh"]
-[Jennifer groans]

1:17:39.250 --> 1:17:41.125
[Aileen gasps]

1:17:41.125 --> 1:17:42.250
[Aileen screams]

1:17:46.708 --> 1:17:48.041
-Oh, Dad. Thank God.

1:17:48.041 --> 1:17:50.333
[Jennifer panting]

1:17:50.333 --> 1:17:51.958
-Oh.

1:17:51.958 --> 1:17:54.833
[Jennifer panting]

1:17:56.208 --> 1:17:57.666
[Lewis] She's gone now, my dear.

1:17:59.416 --> 1:18:01.333
Aileen's gone.

1:18:08.083 --> 1:18:10.291
[Older Aileen] [voice-over]
So... that's how it ended

1:18:10.291 --> 1:18:13.375
for Mrs. Lewis Fell the Second.

1:18:13.375 --> 1:18:17.166
She even got a burial at sea,
which I thought was kinda cool.

1:18:17.166 --> 1:18:18.958
In actuality,
I washed up somewhere

1:18:18.958 --> 1:18:20.458
off the St. Johns River.

1:18:22.208 --> 1:18:24.000
Guess I was lucky
the gators didn't find me

1:18:24.000 --> 1:18:26.875
before some old fisherman did.

1:18:26.875 --> 1:18:29.708
Keith's life insurance money
kept me going for a spell.

1:18:31.375 --> 1:18:32.750
But it didn't last long.

1:18:34.333 --> 1:18:36.291
[car brakes squeaking]

1:18:36.291 --> 1:18:39.375
Before I knew it, I was back
to my old tricks again.

1:18:39.375 --> 1:18:41.000
[car door squeaks]

1:18:46.916 --> 1:18:48.125
-[scoffs] Remember me?

1:18:49.916 --> 1:18:51.541
It's payback time, bitch.

1:18:51.541 --> 1:18:52.708
[Aileen groans]

1:18:54.291 --> 1:18:55.291
[Older Aileen] [voice-over]
Doctors never could

1:18:55.291 --> 1:18:57.416
put my teeth back right.

1:18:57.416 --> 1:19:01.500
Whatever. I like my smile.
I think it gives me character.

1:19:04.208 --> 1:19:06.458
-I'm not doubting that
you were married to Mr. Fell

1:19:06.458 --> 1:19:08.875
for a short period of time.

1:19:08.875 --> 1:19:11.208
But as for the rest
of your story...

1:19:11.208 --> 1:19:13.916
-You mean to tell me
that after all that,

1:19:13.916 --> 1:19:15.875
you still don't
fuckin' believe me?

1:19:15.875 --> 1:19:19.125
-I don't know, Aileen. Should I?

1:19:19.125 --> 1:19:20.958
[bangs table]

1:19:20.958 --> 1:19:23.500
-Well, maybe you should just
figure it out then, huh?

1:19:23.500 --> 1:19:27.916
Peter? A raped woman
got executed

1:19:27.916 --> 1:19:31.416
and used for books
and movies and shit.

1:19:31.416 --> 1:19:34.791
Embellish and stretch the truth,
'cause that's what they all do.

1:19:34.791 --> 1:19:36.750
That's what fuckin' sells!

1:19:38.291 --> 1:19:40.291
They sabotaged my ass!
-[Cop] Time's up here.

1:19:40.291 --> 1:19:43.291
-Society,
the cops, the system!

1:19:43.291 --> 1:19:45.541
Well, fuck you all!

1:19:45.541 --> 1:19:48.291
Fuck 'em all!
-[Cop] A 10-9 in the dayroom.

1:19:48.291 --> 1:19:49.875
Back-up needed.
-[Older Aileen grunts]

1:19:49.875 --> 1:19:51.541
I'm sailin' with the rock,
and I'll be back,

1:19:51.541 --> 1:19:54.125
like Independence Day,
but with Jesus!

1:19:54.125 --> 1:19:55.375
[table crashes]

1:19:55.375 --> 1:19:56.833
[Cop] Calm the fuck down!

1:19:56.833 --> 1:19:59.000
[Older Aileen]
I'll be back on June 6th,

1:19:59.000 --> 1:20:00.625
just like the fuckin' movie!
-[Cop] Come on.

1:20:00.625 --> 1:20:04.375
[Older Aileen]
Big motherfucking ship and all!

1:20:04.375 --> 1:20:05.916
-[Cop] Aileen!
-Thanks, society--

1:20:05.916 --> 1:20:08.166
for railroadin' my ass.
-[Cop] Back up! Back up!

1:20:08.166 --> 1:20:09.583
-I'll be back, goddammit.
-[Cop] Where is the--

1:20:09.583 --> 1:20:12.125
